{
  "texts": [
    "Overall, our results suggest that, although the false positive bias should be kept in mind, ChatGPT may be used-with caution-as a starting point for users looking to gain climate literacy regarding some hazards, like floods and cyclones.",
    "However, considering droughts, more caution should be employed, as false negatives are arguably more dangerous in this context and overall accuracy is lower.",
    "One should naturally ask what the origins of these inaccuracies might be.",
    "While identifying true causes is beyond the scope of this exploratory study, we suggest a few possible factors that may influence the performance of ChatGPT in this context.",
    "First, we must consider that this study was conducted entirely in English."
  ]
}